dct_title_s: Lands of Leland Stanford Junior University [highlighting Searsville Lake Proposal], 1971
dct_description_sm: Map of Stanford University campus and surrounding vicinity depicting Searville Lake Proposal, 28 Apr 1971, indicating boundary lines, creek beds, proposed horse trail, future fencing, and proposed shack riders. Underlying contour map prepared by CAB,  Stanford University Planning Office, 15 Jan 1968, and revised 15 Jun 1970. Also visible: Jasper Ridge Biological Reserve, Outdoor Primate Facility, Stanford Linear Accelerating Center.
